description:
Presenting...  The Tom Cruise Collection (1981-2013), the biggest collection of Tom Cruise films ever made as a torrent.  Here is everything by the actor.  For more on Tom Cruise please go to the following URL: http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tom_Cruise

I have put this entire collection together because Tom Cruise has a lot of good films in his filmography.  The first film he was in he only had a small part but he went on to make lots of movies afterwards where he achieved massive worldwide fame.  Most of them are ripped from Blu Ray, there are a few early ones that are ripped from DVD but that is because there really isn't a Blu Ray version available.  I have done the best job I can, there is a mixture between 720p and 1080p and the same with the audio some are AC3 and some are DTS.  I didn't want to try and make this collection too big in file size so it's not too hard to upload and download etc..  It has arrived at 286 gigabytes which is a pretty good size considering you're getting all his movies.

I know he was in the third Austin Powers movie, Goldmember, but still he only played himself and that doesn't count really and the part was a small introduction part and not a proper movie role.  The movies are all in English, there is no other languages, sorry to all the non English speaking people out there, I have also included English subtitles where I can for the hard of hearing.

It will take a fair while to really get this torrent going but hopefully there will be lots of downloaders and seeders. Tom has got a new movie coming out in 2014, it should be worth looking forward to.  I have encoded them all using the x264 HD codec.  They all look very nice.  If you download this then please help to seed as much as you can, many thanks :-)

